1
00:00:22,200 --> 00:00:23,600
Why are you back again?

2
00:00:24,080 --> 00:00:24,960
Old man,

3
00:00:25,480 --> 00:00:26,600
you look harmless,

4
00:00:26,600 --> 00:00:27,840
but you hide it well.

5
00:00:28,200 --> 00:00:29,260
I don't understand

6
00:00:29,320 --> 00:00:30,480
what you're saying.

7
00:00:31,040 --> 00:00:33,000
The Lu Ban technique is a rare secret art.

8
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:34,460
It has endless mysteries.

9
00:00:34,760 --> 00:00:36,680
Whether it's for blessing or cursing,

10
00:00:36,680 --> 00:00:38,320
as long as it benefits oneself,

11
00:00:38,320 --> 00:00:40,040
there will be a backlash.

12
00:00:40,520 --> 00:00:42,160
And casting the Five Poisons crushing curse

13
00:00:42,160 --> 00:00:43,600
is an even more venomous curse.

14
00:00:43,600 --> 00:00:45,440
The backlash will be even greater.

15
00:00:45,440 --> 00:00:46,320
And you,

16
00:00:46,440 --> 00:00:47,840
took advantage of your apprentice's greed,

17
00:00:47,840 --> 00:00:48,760
making him think

18
00:00:48,760 --> 00:00:49,720
he could use the Five Ghosts

19
00:00:49,720 --> 00:00:51,280
to move Captain Jia's wealth.

20
00:00:51,280 --> 00:00:52,760
But you never told him

21
00:00:53,360 --> 00:00:54,760
it would backfire on him.

22
00:00:55,800 --> 00:00:58,660
What a brilliant move to kill with a borrowed knife.

23
00:00:59,920 --> 00:01:00,760
Actually,

24
00:01:00,840 --> 00:01:01,900
when you came to me,

25
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:03,400
I knew this matter

26
00:01:03,560 --> 00:01:04,640
would be exposed.

27
00:01:05,200 --> 00:01:05,880
So,

28
00:01:06,120 --> 00:01:08,840
I deliberately leaked my disciple's whereabouts.

29
00:01:08,840 --> 00:01:09,760
I understand.

30
00:01:09,920 --> 00:01:10,960
Then Captain Jia

31
00:01:11,080 --> 00:01:13,480
will definitely seek revenge against him.

32
00:01:13,800 --> 00:01:14,520
You thought

33
00:01:15,200 --> 00:01:16,860
you could use your apprentice

34
00:01:16,880 --> 00:01:18,340
to eliminate Captain Jia,

35
00:01:18,600 --> 00:01:20,360
killing two birds with one stone.

36
00:01:20,360 --> 00:01:22,420
With such schemes, being a carpenter

37
00:01:22,880 --> 00:01:24,120
is really a pity.

38
00:01:26,320 --> 00:01:27,160
Young man,

39
00:01:27,320 --> 00:01:28,380
you are too modest.

40
00:01:29,200 --> 00:01:30,860
Then let's see if you can break

41
00:01:30,880 --> 00:01:32,440
my void formation.

42
00:01:32,880 --> 00:01:33,880
Young man,

43
00:01:34,320 --> 00:01:35,360
now you know

44
00:01:35,600 --> 00:01:37,000
that meddling in other people's business

45
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:38,360
is not that easy.

46
00:01:42,520 --> 00:01:44,800
What tricks are you playing now?

47
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:05,500
Be careful, Brother Wang.

48
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:07,460
Insignificant skill.

49
00:02:20,040 --> 00:02:21,560
I will wipe out all of you

50
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:22,490
ghost soldiers.

51
00:02:25,480 --> 00:02:26,320
I'm tired.

52
00:02:26,320 --> 00:02:27,160
I quit.

53
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:31,560
Die.

54
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:39,560
Brother Wang.

55
00:02:39,560 --> 00:02:40,480
Are you okay?

56
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:44,320
Losing to Yingui,

57
00:02:46,760 --> 00:02:48,800
I have nothing to say.

58
00:02:49,640 --> 00:02:51,120
In my whole life,

59
00:02:51,320 --> 00:02:53,520
I only took this one disciple.

60
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:57,680
I taught him all the crafts passed down by Lu Ban.

61
00:02:57,840 --> 00:02:58,920
I told him

62
00:02:59,160 --> 00:03:01,880
to be a decent person before a carpenter,

63
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:03,680
and to have a righteous heart.

64
00:03:03,680 --> 00:03:07,840
But who knew he wanted to hoard the Song family's antiques for himself?

65
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:08,920
For him,

66
00:03:09,160 --> 00:03:11,880
I knelt before everyone and confessed,

67
00:03:12,200 --> 00:03:15,120
and had my legs brutally broken.

68
00:03:15,600 --> 00:03:16,480
And he,

69
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:18,440
abandoned me.

70
00:03:18,480 --> 00:03:20,800
I poured half my life's effort into him,

71
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:22,680
only to find it absurd.

72
00:03:23,480 --> 00:03:24,720
But later,

73
00:03:25,480 --> 00:03:27,400
to get the Luban Technique,

74
00:03:27,920 --> 00:03:30,520
he had the nerve to come back to me,

75
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:32,800
using threats and bribes.

76
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:34,600
For someone like him,

77
00:03:36,040 --> 00:03:39,000
is it possible he won't get his karma?

78
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:41,860
He has already received his due punishment.

79
00:03:42,640 --> 00:03:43,840
And your legs...

80
00:03:46,079 --> 00:03:47,200
Legend says

81
00:03:49,320 --> 00:03:51,560
wherever the Yin Executioner goes,

82
00:03:52,480 --> 00:03:53,600
he will surely

83
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:56,130
clear grievances and eliminate evil.

84
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:58,640
It's a pity

85
00:03:59,760 --> 00:04:02,160
I won't live to see that day.

86
00:04:03,200 --> 00:04:04,440
From now on,

87
00:04:04,880 --> 00:04:06,200
no one will

88
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:07,800
for his sake

89
00:04:08,720 --> 00:04:10,400
resort to

90
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:12,600
extreme measures.

91
00:04:35,159 --> 00:04:36,840
Little Master.

92
00:04:39,960 --> 00:04:41,159
Brother Wang, come.

93
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:43,200
Is the pressure okay?

94
00:04:45,960 --> 00:04:47,000
Don't worry.

95
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:53,280
Listen.

96
00:04:53,840 --> 00:04:55,320
Go find Tang Banxian

97
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:57,800
and ask for an auspicious date and time.

98
00:04:59,200 --> 00:05:00,720
Then use this

99
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:03,840
to scrape off the talisman on the beam,

100
00:05:04,320 --> 00:05:05,840
and the curse will be broken.

101
00:05:05,840 --> 00:05:07,240
As for how to beg him,

102
00:05:08,440 --> 00:05:10,100
I shouldn't have to teach you.

103
00:05:10,880 --> 00:05:12,200
Don't worry.

104
00:05:12,280 --> 00:05:14,210
I will invite him with heavy gifts.

105
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:15,760
Brother Wang,

106
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:17,280
I have other plans.

107
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:18,800
Girl,

108
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:19,600
come in.

109
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:22,080
Let this girl

110
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:23,280
drink with you.

111
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:24,920
I'm leaving.

112
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:26,880
Hurry up.

113
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:30,320
What are you waiting for?

114
00:05:30,320 --> 00:05:30,850
Sit down.

115
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:36,360
For this matter,

116
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:38,050
you take a lot of credit.

117
00:05:38,640 --> 00:05:39,040
Come.

118
00:05:39,520 --> 00:05:40,450
Let me toast you.

119
00:05:42,840 --> 00:05:43,640
Cheers.

120
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:54,080
Brother Wang.

121
00:05:54,880 --> 00:05:56,000
My grandpa said

122
00:05:56,200 --> 00:05:57,680
wherever the Yin Executioner goes,

123
00:05:57,680 --> 00:05:59,010
even if it's pitch dark,

124
00:05:59,120 --> 00:06:00,440
he can clear the clouds and see the sun.

125
00:06:00,440 --> 00:06:01,200
Is it true?

126
00:06:05,720 --> 00:06:06,800
Do you really think

127
00:06:07,320 --> 00:06:08,840
that with one man and one sword,

128
00:06:08,840 --> 00:06:10,400
all the darkness in this world

129
00:06:10,400 --> 00:06:11,480
can be cut away?

130
00:06:14,800 --> 00:06:15,480
However,

131
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:17,650
I have more important things to do.

132
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:19,040
What is it?

133
00:06:19,520 --> 00:06:22,520
Getting married and having children, of course.

134
00:06:29,520 --> 00:06:30,440
Brother Wang.

135
00:06:30,880 --> 00:06:33,010
Please save the people of Taohua Town.

136
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:34,240
As long as

137
00:06:34,880 --> 00:06:36,440
you're willing to help,

138
00:06:36,880 --> 00:06:37,760
I, Yinlian,

139
00:06:38,280 --> 00:06:39,680
will marry you.

140
00:06:40,440 --> 00:06:41,159
Yinlian.

141
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:42,520
Whatever it is,

142
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:43,580
take your time.

143
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:45,080
You don't need to do this.

144
00:06:45,840 --> 00:06:46,480
I'm serious.

145
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:48,280
You really don't have to do this.

146
00:06:51,560 --> 00:06:53,880
I came all the way here several times to testify for you

147
00:06:53,880 --> 00:06:55,159
to get them to let you go.

148
00:06:55,159 --> 00:06:56,020
But look at you,

149
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:57,240
eating, drinking,

150
00:06:57,320 --> 00:06:58,840
and having a beautiful woman keep you company.

151
00:06:58,840 --> 00:07:00,770
You're living quite comfortably.

152
00:07:01,880 --> 00:07:03,280
You care about me so much?

153
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:04,160
What,

154
00:07:04,640 --> 00:07:06,280
are you willing to marry me now?

155
00:07:06,280 --> 00:07:06,840
No.

156
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:08,320
What nonsense are you talking about?

157
00:07:08,320 --> 00:07:09,320
Who wants to marry you?

158
00:07:09,320 --> 00:07:10,440
Leave right now.

159
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:11,920
Leave?

160
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:13,120
I can't do that.

161
00:07:13,640 --> 00:07:15,080
I haven't met

162
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:16,280
the mayor yet.

163
00:07:16,520 --> 00:07:18,250
You still want to see my father?

164
00:07:18,520 --> 00:07:20,380
You are just being unreasonable!

165
00:07:21,080 --> 00:07:21,880
Wang Shiqi,

166
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:23,100
let me tell you,

167
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:24,280
even if all the men

168
00:07:24,280 --> 00:07:25,400
in the world died,

169
00:07:25,480 --> 00:07:26,680
I wouldn't marry you.

170
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:27,840
Miss Su.

171
00:07:28,320 --> 00:07:29,520
Brother Wang is a good man.

172
00:07:29,520 --> 00:07:31,450
You can't talk about him like that.

173
00:07:33,159 --> 00:07:34,040
Brother Wang.

174
00:07:34,440 --> 00:07:35,640
She won't marry you.

175
00:07:35,720 --> 00:07:36,650
I will marry you.

176
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:37,440
Okay?

177
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:40,920
You two,

178
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:43,080
you two are simply unreasonable.

179
00:07:45,200 --> 00:07:46,080
Brother Wang.

180
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:47,159
You two...

181
00:07:56,840 --> 00:07:58,040
Xing Sword draws the moon.

182
00:07:58,040 --> 00:07:59,400
Lend me your power today,

183
00:07:59,400 --> 00:08:01,130
to slay all unrest in the world.

184
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:16,720
She is quite pretty.

185
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:19,120
But she has

186
00:08:20,480 --> 00:08:21,340
quite a temper.

187
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:26,120
This girl

188
00:08:26,320 --> 00:08:27,800
is affected by the water ghost's lust.

189
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:28,440
Looks like

190
00:08:28,640 --> 00:08:29,880
I have to help her out.

191
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:41,880
Miss Su.

192
00:08:41,880 --> 00:08:42,679
Don't worry.

193
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:44,800
I will definitely marry you.

194
00:08:45,040 --> 00:08:46,320
Pervert.

195
00:08:50,480 --> 00:08:52,280
That damn Wang Shiqi

196
00:08:52,680 --> 00:08:55,080
made me so angry I couldn't sleep all night.

197
00:08:55,320 --> 00:08:56,280
Our Taohua Town

198
00:08:56,280 --> 00:08:58,200
is such a great place with good Fengshui.

199
00:08:58,200 --> 00:09:00,130
Yet we got such a loser as our mayor.

200
00:09:00,520 --> 00:09:01,520
Yes.

201
00:09:01,520 --> 00:09:02,680
Look at the whole town,

202
00:09:02,680 --> 00:09:03,840
who respects him?

203
00:09:03,880 --> 00:09:05,400
In my opinion, he can only be obedient

204
00:09:05,400 --> 00:09:06,480
and act as Director Song's dog

205
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:08,140
to keep his position as mayor.

206
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:13,240
How dare you!

207
00:09:13,760 --> 00:09:15,520
How can you gossip about Mayor Su?

208
00:09:15,520 --> 00:09:16,880
If you speak nonsense again,

209
00:09:16,880 --> 00:09:18,810
I'll have my father arrest you all.

210
00:09:26,400 --> 00:09:27,120
Wanrong,

211
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:28,960
don't lower yourself to these unruly peasants.

212
00:09:28,960 --> 00:09:29,960
What do they know?

213
00:09:30,800 --> 00:09:31,400
Wanrong,

214
00:09:31,680 --> 00:09:33,120
Look at the water in Taohua Town,

215
00:09:33,120 --> 00:09:33,850
it's so deep.

216
00:09:33,920 --> 00:09:35,080
Why don't you marry me?

217
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:36,720
If the Song and Su families join forces,

218
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:37,680
this Taohua Town

219
00:09:37,880 --> 00:09:39,120
will be ours.

220
00:09:39,480 --> 00:09:40,940
Your father can rest easy.

221
00:09:41,560 --> 00:09:43,160
Wouldn't that be wonderful?

222
00:09:44,120 --> 00:09:45,120
Mr. Song,

223
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:47,240
I'll tell you one last time.

224
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:48,360
I have absolutely

225
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:49,920
no interest in you.

226
00:09:50,160 --> 00:09:50,920
And my father would never

227
00:09:50,920 --> 00:09:52,880
rely on marriage to secure his position.

228
00:09:52,880 --> 00:09:55,340
He will definitely govern Taohua Town well.

229
00:09:58,960 --> 00:09:59,800
Wanrong,

230
00:09:59,800 --> 00:10:00,680
you

231
00:10:00,760 --> 00:10:02,120
are just too stubborn.

232
00:10:02,680 --> 00:10:04,000
I meant well.

233
00:10:04,400 --> 00:10:05,200
Forget it.

234
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:06,480
For everything before,

235
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:07,560
it's all my fault.

236
00:10:07,680 --> 00:10:08,640
Drink this tea

237
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:09,640
and calm down.

238
00:10:22,520 --> 00:10:23,480
I have things to do.

239
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:24,480
I'll leave first.

240
00:10:28,680 --> 00:10:29,640
What...

241
00:10:30,200 --> 00:10:31,480
What happened to me?

242
00:10:37,680 --> 00:10:38,520
Now,

243
00:10:39,160 --> 00:10:40,640
you have to obey me.
